              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title"> <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion1" href="#collapseTwo1"> Our location <i class="fa fa-angle-right pull-right"></i> </a> </h3>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseTwo1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">We are located at 123 King street Toronto,On</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title"> <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion1" href="#collapseThree1"> How many games are available? <i class="fa fa-angle-right pull-right"></i> </a> </h3>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseThree1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">We have over 12000+ games available, from classics to the newest games we have it all! </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title"> <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion1" href="#collapseFour1"> How to get in contact for an event?<i class="fa fa-angle-right pull-right"></i> </a> </h3>
              </div>
              <div id="collapseFour1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">You can contact us by email,phone or directly in person!</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
